org.hps.record.daqconfig2019

Class FEEPrecaleConfig2019

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.hps.record.daqconfig2019.AbstractConfig2019<Double>
      • org.hps.record.daqconfig2019.FEEPrecaleConfig2019

  • public class FEEPrecaleConfig2019
extends AbstractConfig2019<Double>
    Class FEEPrecaleConfig2019 is an implementation of the abstract AbstractCutConfig2019 for FEE prescale of a region. It provides the means to access this value and, for package classes, set it.
